The paper deals with the quality assurance of machine learning models, which is a topic that falls under the broad category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The specific focus on ensuring monotonicity of the models suggests that the paper could also be classified under machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of verification technology and directed computation of test cases suggests that the paper could also be classified under formal methods (cs.ET) and systems and control (cs.SY).
